{"tid":1983072,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"涉企圖謀殺何君堯　男子精神狀態適合答辯","createTime":"2020-04-21T14:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T15:43:20.000Z","uid":1267,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6f35131504fdf27fe4c4e1d313c925ec445f50d2","tid":1983072,"uid":1267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:38:22.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯去年11月在屯門擺街站派傳單時，一名男子假扮成其支持者上前獻膠花，並涉嫌乘機刺傷何的左胸。該男子因而被控企圖謀殺罪，案件今(21日)在粉嶺法院再訊。被告繼續毋須答辯，控方指精神科醫生認為他適合答辯，申請將案件押後至5月19日，期間要就控罪的適切性和審訊地點諮詢律政司意見。被告沒有保釋申請，須繼續還押監房看管。<br />\n<br />\n報稱無業的被告董栢輝（30歲），被控於2019年11月6日，在屯門湖翠路啟豐花園與海翠花園之間的行人路，企圖謀殺何君堯。<br />\n<br />\n原來佢一路都冇申請過保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0db3cc0006016467e985c505703e723e77ba74a","tid":1983072,"uid":1267,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:39:47.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔會忘記721嘅同時都可以唔好忘記哩個手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd1b07fa79f2895a262eb2b15c8c5dfb4717fbc","tid":1983072,"uid":1267,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"佢已經由上年年尾坐到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e9f206ab80837f1c6e480543b956d02ce8ed70","tid":1983072,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:40:53.000Z","msg":"好多黃絲話係做媒"},{"pid":"6d37343ffd4230f68c821b08199ed1240f9b0125","tid":1983072,"uid":1267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e9f206ab80837f1c6e480543b956d02ce8ed70","tid":1983072,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:40:53.000Z","msg":"好多黃絲話係做媒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"咁同割勇武蓆冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p